## Remarks  
 您可以使用 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.RecognizerInfo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> 对象或对象获取已初始化识别引擎的标识信息 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizerInfo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> 。  
  
 从获取的实例中返回的信息由 " <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> **控制面板**" 的 "**语音属性**" 成员中的设置确定。  
  
 您可以使用的实例 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo> ， <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> 用构造函数构造的特定配置 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.%23ctor%28System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo%29> 。  
  
 静态方法 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.InstalledRecognizers%2A> 以实例的形式返回所有可用 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> 配置的列表 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo> 。  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 下面的示例 <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> 针对允许的 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> 配置（表示为对象列表）验证给定的和标识符字符串 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo> 。  
  
 如果 <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> 和标识符字符串有效，则此示例将创建一个 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> 使用实例作为参数的的新实例 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo> 。  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine SelectRecognizer(CultureInfo requiredCulture, string requiredId)   
{  
  // Select based on a specific recognizer configuration  
  SpeechRecognitionEngine speechRecognitionEngine=null;  
  foreach (RecognizerInfo config in SpeechRecognitionEngine.InstalledRecognizers())   
  {  
    if (config.Culture.Equals(requiredCulture) && config.Id== requiredId)   
    {  
      speechRecognitionEngine = new SpeechRecognitionEngine(config);  
      break;  
    }  
  }  
  return speechRecognitionEngine;  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 下面的示例实现一个按钮单击，该按钮将在中显示对象中的所有信息 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo> <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MessageBox> 。  
  
 返回的实例中包含的键/值对 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo.AdditionalInfo%2A> 连接到一个文本表。  
  
```csharp  
private void recognizerInfoButton_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)   
{  
  RecognizerInfo info = _recognizer.RecognizerInfo;  
  string AudioFormats = "";  
  foreach (SpeechAudioFormatInfo fmt in info.SupportedAudioFormats)   
  {  
    AudioFormats += String.Format("       {0}\n", fmt.EncodingFormat.ToString());  
  }  
  string AdditionalInfo = "";  
  foreach (string key in info.AdditionalInfo.Keys)   
  {  
    AdditionalInfo += String.Format("      {0}: {1}\n", key, info.AdditionalInfo[key]);  
  }  
  MessageBox.Show(String.Format(  
                     "Name:                 {0 } \n" +  
                     "Description:          {1} \n" +  
                     "SupportedAudioFormats:\n" +  
                     " {2} " +  
                     "Culture:              {3} \n" +  
                     "AdditionalInfo:       \n" +  
                     " {4}\n",  
                     info.Name.ToString(),  
                     info.Description.ToString(),  
                     AudioFormats,  
                     info.Culture.ToString(),  
                     AdditionalInfo));  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>对象可以包括区域性的名称、关联的语言、国家/地区、使用的日历以及如何设置日期和排序字符串的格式。  
  
   
  
